
Ex3 - Basic Shell Extended
Authored by Mordechai Goldstein
318530136

==Description==
This program tends to demonstrate how a shell looks alike.
Functionallity:
- regular command running 
- history saving and reusing
- output piping between processes
- command sending to background
- command keep running after terminal quitting
For exit, type "done".

==Program Files==
ex3.c - shell
history.txt - the default history file. created after the first running of the code.
README - this explanation file :) 

==How to compile?==
ex3.c:
    gcc ex3.c -o ex3


